{"tid":511892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一地兩檢】湯家驊：凸顯基本法是「活文件」　陳文敏：改變離法律，要憲法做什麼？","createTime":"2017-12-28T02:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T14:50:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0d3b9e56b608b2d74acd6be5c807cba311fbef","tid":511892,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171228/s00001/0cd952e1d8da5ecf82e58ddfaee39131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171228%2Fs00001%2F0cd952e1d8da5ecf82e58ddfaee39131.jpg&h=2c6b9650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會昨日批准《高鐵西九龍站設立口岸實施「一地兩檢」的合作安排》。行政會議成員湯家驊今早出席港台節目，指人大常委會安排是「凸顯了基本法作為前瞻性的憲政文件，是活的文件」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊強調，有關決定是源於特區政府和廣東省政府，透過國務院向人大常委會作呈請，要求確認「一地兩檢」安排，不是由人大常委會提出，認為有關決定對香港法治絲毫無損。<br />\n<br />\n他認為最重要是相關安排是因應運輸和經濟發展的要求、不會削弱香港地區區域的範圍、和不會影響特區居民日常生活的權利和自由。<br />\n<br />\n港大法律學者陳文敏稍後於同一節目指，「原則是對，憲法是一部活的文件，是會隨時代改變而理解有改變」。但他強調，「這改變始終不離開法律文本，如果不是，還要部憲法來做什麼？憲法不是時代改變就喜歡說什麼就什麼」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171228/s00001/1514426143439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171228%2Fs00001%2F1514426143439&d=Z4JEb5%2BBPZNdO12kQ4Fh1tr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=37bc5a11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171228%2Fs00001%2F1514426143439&h=519b23c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171228/s00001/1514426143439</a>"},{"pid":"5f01465aa96c8bab7b65c1136035a8c2bf8ee43e","tid":511892,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:25:16.000Z","msg":"未成年基本法會發育是常識吧<br />\n<br />\n未成年既啱哂你喇湯渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55920c342fd2d25a17de387721131d57c1d05dee","tid":511892,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:27:31.000Z","msg":"習思想入黨章都係搵D 二打六動議提出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35dd709c875ddc67a9762cfd9cc021317f0ef5c6","tid":511892,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:29:40.000Z","msg":"湯家驊搞細路單野點?"},{"pid":"b7047c2f783968cb255ff29ac3c11e8e61ea8b0a","tid":511892,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"湯大狀做乜成日上鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3d00babce11d4b8797f8eef1ccaf0c2572c88e","tid":511892,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7047c2f783968cb255ff29ac3c11e8e61ea8b0a","tid":511892,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"湯大狀做乜成日上鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"老闆要佢開工<br />\n有得唔開工？<br />\n人地就真係專業5毛啦"},{"pid":"afc0a76d8d67eb91b94d611891aeb6c1007c6927","tid":511892,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"活文件即係共產黨話點就點"},{"pid":"74c4423227d3614698bde06538391336ce464e10","tid":511892,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"其實佢都幾廢，而家撈對家又撈唔起"},{"pid":"49a9c19d8153d63fd57a489ed309dd444f3e8b77","tid":511892,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35dd709c875ddc67a9762cfd9cc021317f0ef5c6","tid":511892,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:29:40.000Z","msg":"湯家驊搞細路單野點?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset